title: Daerius Washington Named SWAC Defensive Player of the Week
text:
Daerius Washington Named SWAC Defensive Player of the Week Tools 
Story Created: Oct 19, 2015 at 6:37 PM CDT 
Another Hornet picked up a couple of weekly honors this week as senior linebacker was named the SWAC and College Sports Madness SWAC Defensive Player of the Week. Washington had a team-high 12 tackles against Arkansas-Pine Bluff and his nine solo stops was a game-high. He also had 1.5 tackles behind the line of scrimmage which lost three yards. Washington had a pass break up and also had a quarterback hurry. On the season Washington is second on the team with 56 total stops. His eight tackles for lost yardage leads the team. He is sixth in the conference in tackles and second in tackles behind the line of scrimmage.
